    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>今天的太阳</p><p>像瘫痪的卡车</p><p>沉重的运走 整个下午</p><p>白醋 春梦 野柚子</p><p>把回忆揣进手掌的血管里</p><p>手电的光透过掌背</p><p>仿佛看见跌入云端的海豚</p><p>—-毕赣 路边野餐</p><div class="botui-container" id="me" style="min-height:300px; padding:2px 6px 4px 6px;  border-radius: 10px; 2px solid">    <center><h4>与 Alkaid 对话中...</h4></center>    <bot-ui>        <center>            <div style="background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: 10em; background-position: center center; height: 10em; background-image: url(&quot;https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Fog-Forest/cdn@1.7/botui/loading.svg&quot;);" class=" lazyloaded" data-bg="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Fog-Forest/cdn@1.7/botui/loading.svg"></div>            <p><a href="javascript:location.reload();" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">♐加载中[如果加载不出请点击刷新页面]♐</a></p>        </center>    </bot-ui></div><p><img src="image.jpg" alt="https://cher112.top/posts/6161fe24.html"></p>]]></content>
    
    
    
